This paper is likely to belong to the Sound (cs.SD) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories as it deals with sound event detection and audio tagging. It also involves the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) research.
